title: First 800kV UHVDC transformer rolls out from ABB India, Vadodara factory (ABB India Limited)
text: ( Source : ABB India Limited ) Vadodara , October 26 , 2015 - This transformer will be installed at POWERGRID's Agra substation, a part of the North East-Agra 800 kV UHVDC transmission link. ABB India rolled out the first 800 kilovolt (kV)
